The Cybersecurity Bootcamp at 4Geeks Academy equips students to become cybersecurity specialists in just 16 weeks, with no prior experience required. The program covers foundational topics in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration while providing hands-on skills in cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. Participants manage risks using data loss prevention strategies and learn to navigate compliance with international standards. Classes consist of three live sessions per week, with a maximum of 16 participants, and are available in English and Spanish. Graduates receive an Official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop